features: Play Food For Toddlers: This 28-piece fruits and vegetables set was a great addition to your girls & boy play kitchen. Includes 1 toy basket, 1 chopping board, 1 pretend knive, and a bulk brightand colorful play foods.

Fake food Playset made of high-end environmentally abs plastic with round edges, durable & safe to play. Realistic detailed each piece of the “food” is, giving toddler accurate representation of what the real food looks like.

The cooking food comes in a durable shopping basket that can carry and store it in. Great for your little one to learn different food items and have the ability to play grocery store while never leaving the house!

Each piece of fruit or vegetable are great size for toddler hands and can be cut using the included plastic knive. The sticky pad is strong to “cut” them and played repeatedly. Keeps your littles engaged for a long time.

Great for development hand/eye coordination with “cutting”. Used to learn shapes, colors, matching, fine motor etc. Suitable for pretend cooking play, daycare supplies, New Year's/Christmas/Birthday gift, Classroom learning toy for ages 3+ year
